{"tid":904960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[369]【還看珠西】港珠澳大橋業務拖累 冠忠巴士發盈警料少賺六成","createTime":"2018-11-16T18:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T01:28:13.000Z","uid":20058,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"360a1f37a150bc132b5109a0ad3b5e5890242905","tid":904960,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"冠忠巴士（0306）發盈警，預期截至今年9月底止中期純利將不多於4000萬元，意味上半年純利將大跌超過六成。集團解釋，上半年盈利大跌，除因為欠缺出售資產的特殊收益、油價推升成本外，集團期內因港珠澳大橋開通開展跨境巴士業務造成巨大開支，亦是盈警主因之一。<br />\n<br />\n冠忠表示，港珠澳大橋開業成本包括採購額外巴士產生較大的折舊支出、租用跨境巴士配額、司機招聘、培訓以及宣傳開支等；同時集團去年上半年因出售錄得5900萬元非經常性收益，推高基數下令今年上半年收益按年下滑。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋上月開通，在大量過境遊客湧入在東涌造成交通擠塞及混亂，冠忠主席黃良柏早前曾現身「護航」，表示不應單看一天或一個月的情況，相信有關路線將會大受市民歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1542380558709&amp;issue=20181116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1542380558709%26issue%3D20181116&d=6c610CMsiqVX8lnycmZZX7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=38161a2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1542380558709&amp;issue=20181116</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48d80d2968501796d5ec08b06171c31b24c45db","tid":904960,"uid":115451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T18:30:36.000Z","msg":"豬頭骨 <br />\n架車入面有屎有尿應該日日都發生"},{"pid":"fcf830bccee3e4a74904734628983ce2b25f61a5","tid":904960,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"炒業績<br />\n前兩日股價飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e42ff6b737bd1c1bcda719288789ccab2258fd0","tid":904960,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T21:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smil